paidy_super_ai module¶

paidy_super_ai.calculate_risk_score(email_address: str) → float¶

Calculates a score between 0.0 (high risk) and 1.0 (low risk) for a given consumer email-address.

Raises an exception in case provided email-address is invalid.

paidy_super_ai.create_superai_robot() → robot.Robot¶

Creates and returns a robot with PaidySuperAI Technology.
